{"tw": {"3099630": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "網球天使", "steam_appid": 3099630, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>💟OUR NEW GAME💟</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/5e7fdd040ebd686617739d166b91c31b.avif?t=1764757827\" width=620 height=226 /></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/2267f6e12ca11d4d1568f8274b5bded0.avif?t=1764757827\" width=600 height=279 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/f24240339abef00af6ce3e99f8cfcd39.avif?t=1764757827\" width=141 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Academy Love Saga: Tennis Angels</strong>是一款具有動態動作導向遊戲玩法的網球遊戲。控制可愛的女孩們，通過戰略定位和巧妙使用特殊技能，參與令人興奮的比賽。享受一個退休網球教練如何重拾昔日輝煌的搞笑故事。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/3f2896466628be577e6d53565e44591b.avif?t=1764757827\" width=552 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用蓄力擊球將球完美地打入對手的場地，或者衝到網前進行激烈的近距離戰鬥，冒著對手巧妙挑高球的風險？另外，要注意你的體力，因為一旦耗盡，你會陷入嚴重的困境。積累足夠的緊張度，釋放特殊技能，壓倒對手。在這款挑戰性遊戲中測試你的技術和智慧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/54c6f6df922b3341753a1df27e45aad9.poster.avif?t=1764757827\" width=620 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/54c6f6df922b3341753a1df27e45aad9.webm?t=1764757827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/54c6f6df922b3341753a1df27e45aad9.mp4?t=1764757827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/60a2040c030043ab4ee800d5b06462de.avif?t=1764757827\" width=434 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升角色等級以增加她們的屬性，並解鎖新的強大技能在比賽中使用。購買適合她們玩法的裝備。在戰役模式中有多個角色，不同的屬性成長和技能需要你解鎖。嘗試不同的角色，選擇最適合你玩法的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/d331c3b4cc127ed25545a93117490fa8.poster.avif?t=1764757827\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/d331c3b4cc127ed25545a93117490fa8.webm?t=1764757827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/d331c3b4cc127ed25545a93117490fa8.mp4?t=1764757827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/47cf3d2161e6b5f1916ec9f7bf361000.avif?t=1764757827\" width=472 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >對於喜歡遊戲劇情的玩家 - 我們在這款遊戲中有許多“情節”（是的，兩種類型的情節）。體驗一個不受歡迎的教練贏得他美麗的女性俱樂部成員的認可（和心）的有趣而戲劇性的故事。每個角色也都有自己的“愛情故事”，可以隨著訓練和升級逐漸解鎖。要抓住…… 咳 訓練她們所有人！！！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/67abe94525f400d3395fe6ec05d2b92c.poster.avif?t=1764757827\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic