uble when it runs out. With enough Tension, unleash special skills and overwhelm your opponent. Test both your skill and your mind in this challenging game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/54c6f6df922b3341753a1df27e45aad9.poster.avif?t=1764757827\" width=620 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/54c6f6df922b3341753a1df27e45aad9.webm?t=1764757827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/54c6f6df922b3341753a1df27e45aad9.mp4?t=1764757827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/ef815df5685068dea1ad2b7e649efba4.avif?t=1764757827\" width=452 height=140 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/39f2e12bce85b7e4925422b8c4cd3258.poster.avif?t=1764757827\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/39f2e12bce85b7e4925422b8c4cd3258.webm?t=1764757827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099630/extras/39f2e12bce85b7e4925422b8c4cd3258.mp4?t=1764757827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up your characters to increase their stats and unlock new powerful skills to use in the match. Purchase suitable equipment to complement their playstyle. There are multiple characters with different stat growths and skills that